.\" Manpage for Simple Shell.
.TH _SHELL 1 "22 December 2023" "Version 1.0"

.SH NAME
.SS Simple Shell - create a simple shell to used in C language 

.SH SYNOPSIS
.SS ./hsh [options] [command | file]

.SH DESCRIPTION
.SS The simple shell in C is a basic command-line interpreter that allows users to interact with the operating system by entering commands.

.SH COMMAND
.SS .B env - built-in command that prints the current environment

.SS .B exit - built-in command that prints exit the shell

.SS .B ls - list the content of current directory

...

.SH EXAMPLES
.SS at current terminal, echo "ls" | ./hsh

It shows the ls command non-interactively

.SS in shell terminal (after executing ./hsh), ls -l

It shows the ls command with flag -l

.SS in shell terminal (after executing ./hsh), exit
 
It exits the program

.SH AUTHOR
.SS Gab Martin
.SS Tuyen Huynh